---
import banner from "@/src/assets/images/banners/Emerging_Tech_Banner.png";
import PageLayout from "@/src/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import base_url from "@/src/lib/base_url";
---

<PageLayout title="Where Can AI Advance Transportation" bannerImage={banner}>
  <Fragment slot="banner">Artificial Intelligence (AI)</Fragment>
  <main>
    <h2>Where Can AI Advance Transportation</h2>
    <p>
      Artificial Intelligence serves as a transformative "intelligence layer" for the surface transportation system, moving the needle from traditional, retrospective analysis to a future of real-time
      awareness and predictive foresight. By integrating AI, agencies can harness the true value of their data to drive higher-quality decisions.
    </p>

    <!-- Main Section -->
    <div class="row ai-card-row">
      <div class="col-lg-2 ai-header-col">
        <h3>Real-Time Data and Adaptive Operations</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-10 p-4 d-flex gap-4 flex-column">
        <!-- Real-Time Data Section -->
        <div>
          <p>
            A key value of AI lies in its ability to digest and interpret massive streams of real-time data that are otherwise impossible for humans to monitor at scale. In operations and safety, this
            means moving from observing what happened to predicting what is about to occur. AI enables systems to sense emerging risks (such as erratic vehicle behavior or a sudden shift in weather)
            and trigger immediate, automated responses. Whether it is adjusting signal timing to clear a sudden bottleneck or alerting a transit operator to a potential conflict, AI can help ensure
            that multimodal systems are constantly adapting to the live environment to maximize safety and efficiency.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Predictive Intelligence Subsection -->
        <div class="card data-card shadow-sm card-body card-gray">
          <h5 class="card-title">Predictive Intelligence and Strategic Decision-Making</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            Beyond the "here and now," AI offers unparalleled predictive opportunities that can strengthen long-term planning, asset management, and project delivery. By identifying complex patterns
            within historical and cross-cutting datasets, AI allows agencies to forecast infrastructure needs with greater potential accuracy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Application Cards -->
        <div class="card data-card shadow-sm card-body card-gray">
          <h5 class="card-title">Data-Driven Planning</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            AI simulates thousands of "what-if" scenarios to help planners understand how new infrastructure or a freight corridor will impact regional performance and economic vitality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card data-card shadow-sm card-body card-gray">
          <h5 class="card-title">Predictive Asset Management</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            Rather than relying on static lifecycles, AI enables a more strategic approach to infrastructure health. By predicting exactly when a bridge or pavement section will require intervention,
            agencies can optimize long-term investments and extend the life of critical assets.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card data-card shadow-sm card-body card-gray">
          <h5 class="card-title">Mission Optimization</h5>
          <p class="card-text">AI streamlines internal agency operations, from automating administrative workflows to optimizing project delivery timelines.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Conclusion -->
        <p>
          Ultimately, AI empowers agencies to shift from a reactive posture to a proactive management model, ensuring that every dollar invested results in a safer, more resilient, and more efficient
          transportation system.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .ai-header-col {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: start;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #055681 0%, #01121b 100%);
      padding: 1rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .ai-header-col h3 {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: white;
      text-transform: none;
    }

    .ai-card-row {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      border: 1px solid #e7edf3;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ai-card-row p {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      border: 1px solid #d1e7f7;
      border-radius: 0.4rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .card-gray {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
    }

    .card-gray p {
      color: black;
    }

    .card-gray h5 {
      color: #055681;
    }

    .card-gray h5:after {
      display: none;
      content: "";
    }
  </style>
</PageLayout>
